      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3, a superlative example of the E46 chassis. This specimen features the legendary S54B32 power unit, showing exceptional oil analysis results and precise valve clearances. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G six-speed manual and a variable M-differential lock, both functioning with factory-new tactility. Significant preventative measures have been addressed, including structural subframe reinforcement and a full cooling system overhaul using high-flow components. The suspension retains its original kinematics with refreshed dampers and bushings, ensuring the sharp turn-in and neutral handling balance characteristic of this homologation-bred icon. Every factory seal is intact, and the undercarriage is free of fluid weeping or oxidation. This is a definitive, mechanically transparent example for the serious enthusiast.",
